About Us
GEEKSFORLESS EUROPE sp. z o.o.
GeeksForLess is a Global outsourcing company with the Global; Headquarters in Toronto, Canada and its skilled workforce across our delivery offices in Europe, Americas, Asia and the Middle East.
GeeksForLess is established as a business partner, delivering IT human resources and Professional Services to European and North American companies seeking specialized software development, Technical Support, QA testing, Information Security, Web design, Web development, System Administration and other time-consuming administrative services. We deliver top quality Outsourcing Services to companies, at the same time allowing to reduce dramatically HR related costs. Offshore software developers and other IT personnel give companies the opportunity to tap into highly technically educated personnel with excellent work ethics at a lower cost while being able to integrate and manage them as an extension of their local teams. This allows the companies to achieve high productivity without any loss of control.
Our goal is to provide the world class IT outsourcing of highly skilled and technically-experienced staff to our customers as an extension of their teams and provide exceptional career opportunities for our employees.
At present time, GeeksForLess is serving over 60 clients including small, emerging companies and industry leading corporations in Finance, Healthcare, Construction, Security and Tech industries:
