• Peoples Group – financial product and services provider;
• Aecon – construction company in Canada, providing services in three core segments of Infrastructure, Energy, and Mining;
• Hometrust Company – financial product and services provider;
• Saint Elizabeth Health Care – health care services provider;
• CYREN – cloud-based internet security services;
• Hostopia Inc – private-label wholesale hosting provider;
• DELL – technology solutions, services & support;
• Skybox security – cybersecurity management and analytics;
• Embarcadero Technologies – provider of award-winning tools for application developers and database professionals.
Our flexible partnership model allows our partners to choose a service plan most suitable for their needs, from a single IT person to a large-scale team of hundreds of IT professionals.
